OL,3,CBattle of Flowers finances show 1,000%
OL,4,Cincrease in spending on entertainment
OL,6,FJersey's last Battle of Flowers made a
OL,7,Fmore than #350,000 loss, according to
OL,8,Ftheir financial records.
OL,10,FITV Channel News has been sent a copy
OL,11,Fof last year's accounts, detailing how
OL,12,Fmoney was spent in 2023 and 2024.
OL,14,FRecords found more than #153,700 was
OL,15,Fspent on entertainment such as
OL,16,Fheadline act Sam Ryder - a 1000%
OL,17,Fincrease compared to just under #1,500
OL,18,Fspent in 2023.
OL,20,FThis is shown as 'little gigs' on the
OL,21,Fexpense report.
