OL,6,FFinancial accounts also show that the
OL,7,Fevent made a net deficit in the past
OL,8,Ftwo years, with almost #745,000 spent
OL,9,Foverall in 2024.
OL,11,FIt comes after the strategy group set
OL,12,Fup to save the event said that
OL,13,Ffinancial and leadership issues proved
OL,14,F"insurmountable".
OL,16,FThe group said extensive efforts -
OL,17,Fincluding "intensive discussions with
OL,18,Fgovernment ministers and officials" -
OL,19,Ffailed to secure Battle's future.
